#rstats #rshiny debugging tip.
Use {boomer} to log to the console everything that happens inside reactive calls.
Instead of
foo <- reactive({...})
Do
foo <- reactive(boom({...}))
Adjust the print arg if needed, use the clock arg to profile steps.
